<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CFA4 · TDT230 — Practice Quiz (S.07–S.21)</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg: #0b0e14;
  --bg2: #11151f;
  --card: #161b27;
  --card2: #1b2130;
  --border: #2a3142;
  --text: #e6e9f0;
  --text-dim: #9aa3b8;
  --text-dimmer: #6b7390;
  --blue: #3b82f6;
  --purple: #8b5cf6;
  --green: #10b981;
  --orange: #f59e0b;
  --red: #ef4444;
  --cyan: #06b6d4;
  --correct-bg: rgba(16,185,129,.15);
  --correct-border: #10b981;
  --wrong-bg: rgba(239,68,68,.15);
  --wrong-border: #ef4444;
  --radius: 14px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
body{
  margin:0;
  background:var(--bg);
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, rgba(59,130,246,0.08), transparent 50%),
                     radial-gradient(circle at 80% 100%, rgba(139,92,246,0.08), transparent 50%);
  color:var(--text);
  font-family:'Be Vietnam Pro', system-ui, sans-serif;
  min-height:100vh;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}
.wrap{max-width:920px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px 16px 80px;}

/* ===== HEADER ===== */
.app-header{
  text-align:center;
  padding:28px 16px 22px;
  position:relative;
}
.app-header h1{
  font-size:1.5rem;
  font-weight:800;
  margin:0 0 6px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
  -webkit-background-clip:text;
  background-clip:text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}
.app-header p{
  color:var(--text-dim);
  font-size:.85rem;
  margin:0;
}
.app-header .badge{
  display:inline-block;
  margin-top:10px;
  font-size:.72rem;
  color:var(--text-dimmer);
  background:var(--card2);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:4px 12px;
  border-radius:20px;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}

/* ===== STATS BAR (home) ===== */
.stats-bar{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:10px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}
.stat-box{
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:14px 10px;
  text-align:center;
}
.stat-box .num{font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--blue);}
.stat-box .lbl{font-size:.68rem; color:var(--text-dim); margin-top:2px;}

/* ===== MODULE CARDS (home screen) ===== */
.module-grid{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;}
.module-card{
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:16px 18px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform .15s, border-color .15s, box-shadow .15s;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:14px;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.module-card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-2px);
  border-color:var(--mc, var(--blue));
  box-shadow:0 8px 24px -8px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
}
.module-card .num-chip{
  flex:0 0 auto;
  width:48px; height:48px;
  border-radius:12px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-weight:800; font-size:.95rem;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
}
.module-card .info{flex:1; min-width:0;}
.module-card .info .title{font-weight:700; font-size:.97rem; margin-bottom:3px;}
.module-card .info .sub{font-size:.76rem; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.4;}
.module-card .meta{
  flex:0 0 auto;
  text-align:right;
  font-size:.72rem;
  color:var(--text-dimmer);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
.module-card .meta .qcount{display:block; font-weight:700; color:var(--text);}
.module-card .progress-bar{
  position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; height:3px;
  background:var(--mc, var(--blue));
  transition:width .3s;
}

/* ===== ACTION BUTTONS ===== */
.action-row{display:flex; gap:10px; margin:18px 0; flex-wrap:wrap;}
.btn{
  font-family:inherit;
  font-size:.84rem;
  font-weight:600;
  padding:11px 18px;
  border-radius:10px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  background:var(--card2);
  color:var(--text);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .15s;
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px;
}
.btn:hover{border-color:var(--blue); background:rgba(59,130,246,.1);}
.btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#2563eb); border:none; color:#fff;}
.btn.primary:hover{filter:brightness(1.1); transform:translateY(-1px);}
.btn.danger:hover{border-color:var(--red); background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);}
.btn.full{width:100%; justify-content:center;}
.btn:disabled{opacity:.4; cursor:not-allowed;}

/* ===== QUIZ SCREEN ===== */
.quiz-header{
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
  margin-bottom:16px; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.quiz-header .back-btn{
  background:none; border:none; color:var(--text-dim);
  font-size:.85rem; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px;
  font-family:inherit; padding:6px 0;
}
.quiz-header .back-btn:hover{color:var(--text);}
.quiz-title-block{text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;}
.quiz-title-block h2{font-size:1.15rem; margin:0 0 4px; font-weight:700;}
.quiz-title-block .sub{font-size:.78rem; color:var(--text-dim);}

.progress-track{
  height:8px; background:var(--card2); border-radius:6px; overflow:hidden;
  margin-bottom:6px; border:1px solid var(--border);
}
.progress-fill{height:100%; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6); transition:width .3s; border-radius:6px;}
.progress-label{
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between;
  font-size:.72rem; color:var(--text-dimmer);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.q-card{
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:22px 20px;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}
.q-tag{
  display:inline-block;
  font-size:.68rem;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  color:var(--text-dimmer);
  background:var(--card2);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:3px 10px;
  border-radius:20px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.q-text{
  font-size:1rem;
  line-height:1.6;
  white-space:pre-wrap;
  margin-bottom:18px;
  font-weight:500;
}
.q-text b{color:var(--blue);}

.opt-list{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;}
.opt{
  display:flex;
  align-items:flex-start;
  gap:12px;
  background:var(--card2);
  border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:11px;
  padding:13px 15px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .15s;
  font-size:.92rem;
  line-height:1.5;
}
.opt:hover:not(.locked){border-color:var(--blue); background:rgba(59,130,246,.08);}
.opt .opt-letter{
  flex:0 0 auto;
  width:26px; height:26px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--border);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-weight:700; font-size:.78rem;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
.opt.selected{border-color:var(--blue); background:rgba(59,130,246,.12);}
.opt.correct{border-color:var(--correct-border); background:var(--correct-bg);}
.opt.correct .opt-letter{background:var(--correct-border); color:#fff;}
.opt.wrong{border-color:var(--wrong-border); background:var(--wrong-bg);}
.opt.wrong .opt-letter{background:var(--wrong-border); color:#fff;}
.opt.locked{cursor:default;}
.opt.dim{opacity:.5;}

.explain-box{
  margin-top:16px;
  padding:14px 16px;
  border-radius:11px;
  background:var(--bg2);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-left:3px solid var(--cyan);
  font-size:.86rem;
  line-height:1.6;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  display:none;
}
.explain-box.show{display:block; animation:fadeIn .25s;}
.explain-box .lbl{
  font-weight:700;
  color:var(--cyan);
  font-size:.74rem;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:.5px;
  margin-bottom:6px;
  display:block;
}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(-4px);} to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}}

.nav-row{
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; margin-top:18px;
}

/* ===== RESULT SCREEN ===== */
.result-hero{
  text-align:center;
  padding:30px 20px;
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  margin-bottom:20px;
}
.result-hero .score-circle{
  width:140px; height:140px;
  border-radius:50%;
  margin:0 auto 16px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  flex-direction:column;
  border:6px solid var(--border);
  position:relative;
}
.result-hero .score-circle .pct{font-size:2rem; font-weight:800;}
.result-hero .score-circle .frac{font-size:.78rem; color:var(--text-dim); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.result-hero .verdict{font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;}
.result-hero .verdict-sub{font-size:.82rem; color:var(--text-dim);}

.review-list{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;}
.review-item{
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-left:4px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:11px;
  padding:14px 16px;
  font-size:.85rem;
  cursor:pointer;
}
.review-item.ok{border-left-color:var(--correct-border);}
.review-item.bad{border-left-color:var(--wrong-border);}
.review-item .ri-top{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:6px;}
.review-item .ri-q{color:var(--text-dim); font-size:.8rem; line-height:1.5;}
.review-item .ri-icon{font-size:1rem;}

/* ===== FILTER CHIPS ===== */
.filter-row{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:16px;}
.chip-filter{
  font-size:.76rem; padding:7px 14px; border-radius:20px;
  background:var(--card2); border:1px solid var(--border);
  color:var(--text-dim); cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;
  transition:all .15s;
}
.chip-filter.active{background:var(--blue); border-color:var(--blue); color:#fff;}

/* ===== TOAST ===== */
.toast{
  position:fixed; bottom:24px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
  background:var(--card2); border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:12px 22px; border-radius:30px; font-size:.85rem;
  opacity:0; transition:all .3s; z-index:999;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
}
.toast.show{opacity:1; transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0);}

.hidden{display:none !important;}
.center-empty{text-align:center; padding:60px 20px; color:var(--text-dimmer);}
.center-empty .emoji{font-size:2.5rem; margin-bottom:10px;}

footer.app-footer{
  text-align:center;
  color:var(--text-dimmer);
  font-size:.72rem;
  margin-top:30px;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}

@media (max-width:480px){
  .module-card{padding:13px 14px;}
  .module-card .num-chip{width:40px; height:40px; font-size:.8rem;}
  .q-card{padding:17px 14px;}
  .result-hero .score-circle{width:115px; height:115px;}
  .result-hero .score-circle .pct{font-size:1.6rem;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap" id="app">
  <div class="app-header">
    <h1>📊 CFA4 · TDT230 — Practice Quiz</h1>
    <p>CFA Institute Standard Multiple Choice · Session 1 → Session 6</p>
    <div class="badge">PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT MODULE · 151 QUESTIONS</div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ HOME SCREEN ============ -->
  <div id="screen-home">
    <div class="stats-bar">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="num" id="stat-total">107</div><div class="lbl">Total Questions</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="num" id="stat-done">0</div><div class="lbl">Attempted</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="num" id="stat-avg">—</div><div class="lbl">Avg Accuracy</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-row">
      <button class="btn primary full" onclick="startFullTest()">🚀 Full Test — 151 Câu (Randomized)</button>
    </div>
    <div class="action-row">
      <button class="btn" onclick="startWeakReview()">🎯 Review Wrong Answers</button>
      <button class="btn danger" onclick="resetProgress()">🗑️ Reset Progress</button>
    </div>

    <div class="module-grid" id="module-grid"></div>

    <footer class="app-footer">CFA Level 4 / TDT230 · Loc Truong CFA · Questions © CFA Institute</footer>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ QUIZ SCREEN ============ -->
  <div id="screen-quiz" class="hidden">
    <div class="quiz-header">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="exitQuiz()">← Back</button>
      <button class="btn" style="font-size:.74rem; padding:7px 12px;" onclick="toggleQuizMenu()">⋮ Options</button>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-title-block">
      <h2 id="quiz-title">—</h2>
      <div class="sub" id="quiz-sub">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
    <div class="progress-label">
      <span id="progress-text">Câu 1 / 1</span>
      <span id="progress-score">✓ 0 · ✗ 0</span>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" id="q-card">
      <div class="q-tag" id="q-tag">—</div>
      <div class="q-text" id="q-text">—</div>
      <div class="opt-list" id="opt-list"></div>
      <div class="explain-box" id="explain-box">
        <span class="lbl">💡 Explanation (EN)</span>
        <div id="explain-text"></div>
        <span class="lbl" style="margin-top:10px; display:block; color:#f59e0b;">🗣️ Giải thích dễ hiểu (VN)</span>
        <div id="explain-text-vn" style="font-style:italic;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-row">
      <button class="btn" id="btn-prev" onclick="prevQuestion()">← Prev</button>
      <button class="btn primary" id="btn-next" onclick="nextQuestion()">Câu tiếp →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ RESULT SCREEN ============ -->
  <div id="screen-result" class="hidden">
    <div class="quiz-header">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="goHome()">← Home</button>
    </div>
    <div class="result-hero">
      <div class="score-circle" id="score-circle">
        <div class="pct" id="result-pct">0%</div>
        <div class="frac" id="result-frac">0/0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="verdict" id="result-verdict">—</div>
      <div class="verdict-sub" id="result-sub">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-row">
      <button class="btn primary" onclick="reviewMistakes()">📋 Review Mistakes</button>
      <button class="btn" onclick="retrySame()">🔁 Retry This Set</button>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-row" id="result-filter">
      <button class="chip-filter active" data-f="all" onclick="setReviewFilter('all')">All</button>
      <button class="chip-filter" data-f="bad" onclick="setReviewFilter('bad')">❌ Wrong</button>
      <button class="chip-filter" data-f="ok" onclick="setReviewFilter('ok')">✅ Correct</button>
    </div>
    <div class="review-list" id="review-list"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="toast" id="toast"></div>
</div>

<script>
// MODULE 1: Portfolio Risk and Return - Part I (30 questions)

const MODULE_7 = {
  id: "m7",
  title: "S.07 · Fixed-Income Features & Types",
  subtitle: "Bond Features · Covenants · Embedded Options · Bond Types",
  color: "#06b6d4",
  questions: [
    {
      q: "Step-up coupon bonds are best described as bonds whose:",
      options: ["coupon rate decreases over time.", "coupon rate increases according to a predetermined schedule.", "principal value changes with inflation."],
      correct: 1,
      explanation: "B is correct. Step-up coupon bonds have coupon rates that increase (step up) at predetermined dates specified in the bond indenture.",
      explanationVN: "Step-up coupon bond là trái phiếu có lãi suất coupon tăng dần theo lịch sẵn định trước. Đây là điểm khác biệt so với bond thường có coupon cố định."
    },
    {
      q: "Leveraged loans are loans made primarily to:",
      options: ["sovereign governments.", "lower-credit-quality borrowers.", "central banks."],
      correct: 1,
      explanation: "B is correct. Leveraged loans are loans made to borrowers with below-investment-grade credit quality — often used to finance leveraged buyouts or acquisitions.",
      explanationVN: "Leveraged loans là các khoản vay dành cho công ty có chất lượng tín dụng thấp (dưới mức investment grade), thường dùng trong các thương vụ mua lại bằng đòn bẩy (LBO)."
    },
    {
      q: "A credit-linked note is a bond whose coupon payments depend on the issuer's:",
      options: ["dividend policy.", "stock price.", "credit quality or credit rating."],
      correct: 2,
      explanation: "C is correct. A credit-linked note (CLN) pays higher coupon if a specific credit event (e.g., downgrade, default) does NOT occur. The coupon or principal is linked to the credit performance of a reference entity.",
      explanationVN: "Credit-linked note là trái phiếu mà coupon hoặc gốc liên kết với sự kiện tín dụng của một bên tham chiếu — ví dụ nếu bên đó vỡ nợ, nhà đầu tư có thể mất một phần gốc."
    },
    {
      q: "A payment-in-kind (PIK) bond allows the issuer to:",
      options: ["repay principal early.", "convert debt into equity.", "pay interest using additional bonds instead of cash."],
      correct: 2,
      explanation: "C is correct. A PIK bond allows the issuer to pay periodic interest by issuing additional bonds rather than making cash payments, preserving cash during difficult periods.",
      explanationVN: "PIK bond cho phép issuer trả lãi bằng cách phát hành thêm trái phiếu thay vì trả tiền mặt — giúp công ty giữ lại tiền mặt khi gặp khó khăn, nhưng làm tăng nợ tổng."
    },
    {
      q: "Green bonds are primarily associated with:",
      options: ["environmental or sustainability goals.", "floating-rate coupons.", "high-yield financing."],
      correct: 0,
      explanation: "A is correct. Green bonds are designated bonds where proceeds are used to fund projects with environmental or sustainability benefits, such as renewable energy or clean transportation.",
      explanationVN: "Green bonds là trái phiếu mà tiền thu được dùng để tài trợ cho các dự án thân thiện môi trường như năng lượng tái tạo, giao thông sạch. Không liên quan đến floating rate hay high yield."
    },
    {
      q: "Treasury Inflation-Protected Securities (TIPS) are best described as:",
      options: ["floating-rate corporate bonds.", "U.S. inflation-linked government bonds.", "subordinated leveraged loans."],
      correct: 1,
      explanation: "B is correct. TIPS are U.S. government bonds where the principal is adjusted for inflation based on the Consumer Price Index (CPI). The coupon rate is fixed, but it is applied to the inflation-adjusted principal.",
      explanationVN: "TIPS là trái phiếu chính phủ Mỹ mà phần gốc (principal) được điều chỉnh theo chỉ số CPI. Coupon rate cố định nhưng áp dụng lên principal đã điều chỉnh, nên cả coupon lẫn trả gốc đều được bảo vệ khỏi lạm phát."
    },
    {
      q: "A callable bond gives the issuer the right to:",
      options: ["convert the bond into equity.", "redeem the bond before maturity.", "increase the coupon rate automatically."],
      correct: 1,
      explanation: "B is correct. A callable bond includes an embedded call option that gives the issuer the right to redeem (call back) the bond at a specified price before the stated maturity date. Issuers typically exercise this right when interest rates fall, allowing them to refinance at a lower borrowing cost.",
      explanationVN: "Callable bond có embedded call option cho phép issuer mua lại trái phiếu trước khi đến hạn. Issuer thường thực hiện điều này khi lãi suất thị trường giảm — giúp họ tái cấp vốn rẻ hơn."
    },
    {
      q: "Compared with an otherwise identical straight bond, a putable bond will most likely have:",
      options: ["lower price and higher yield.", "higher price and lower yield.", "the same price and yield."],
      correct: 1,
      explanation: "B is correct. A putable bond gives the bondholder the right to sell the bond back to the issuer at a specified price. This embedded put option is valuable to the investor and therefore commands a higher price (and lower yield) compared with an identical straight bond.",
      explanationVN: "Putable bond cho phép nhà đầu tư bán lại bond cho issuer khi lãi suất tăng. Quyền này có giá trị, nên putable bond phải có giá cao hơn và yield thấp hơn so với straight bond tương đương."
    },
    {
      q: "Convertible bonds allow bondholders to:",
      options: ["exchange bonds for common shares.", "redeem bonds before maturity.", "increase coupon payments periodically."],
      correct: 0,
      explanation: "A is correct. Convertible bonds give the bondholder the right to exchange the bond for a specified number of shares of common stock of the issuer at a pre-set conversion price.",
      explanationVN: "Convertible bond cho phép nhà đầu tư chuyển đổi bond thành cổ phiếu thường theo một tỷ lệ quy định (conversion ratio). Đây là embedded option có giá trị khi giá cổ phiếu tăng."
    },
    {
      q: "A bond with $1,000 par value and a conversion price of $40 has a conversion ratio of:",
      options: ["20 shares.", "25 shares.", "40 shares."],
